# Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in the real values.
**Never commit `.env` to git.**

```bash
# ─── Server ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PORT=4000
NODE_ENV=development          # development | production

# ─── Database ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PostgreSQL connection string (Neon, Supabase, etc.)
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST/DB?sslmode=require

# ─── Auth ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# REQUIRED — must be at least 32 random characters in production
JWT_SECRET=change-me-to-a-long-random-string
JWT_ACCESS_TTL=1h
JWT_REFRESH_TTL_DAYS=30

# ─── Google OAuth ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-google-client-secret
GOOGLE_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:4000/api/auth/google/callback
OAUTH_DEFAULT_EXTENSION_REDIRECT_URI=

# ─── CORS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Comma-separated allowed origins. Do NOT use * in production.
CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5173

# ─── Request limits ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
REQUEST_BODY_LIMIT=2mb

# ─── OpenAI ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# ─── SEMrush webhook (n8n) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
SEMRUSH_URL=https://your-n8n-host.com/webhook/page-keyword-and-traffic
SEMRUSH_LOG_FULL_RESPONSE=false
AHREFS_URL=https://your-n8n-host.com/webhook/ahrefs-domain-keywords

# ─── Queue / Redis ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_URL=redis://127.0.0.1:6379
QUEUE_WORKERS_ENABLED=true
```
